        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 4 at 5:36PM CDT until August 4 at 6:00PM CDT by NWS San Angelo TX</headline>
        <description>At 535 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Mertzon, moving
southeast at 10 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
southwestern Tom Green and southeastern Irion Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
